entry.title: REF CAM | MLS All-Stars vs Arsenal

media:group.media:title: REF CAM | MLS All-Stars vs Arsenal
media:group.media:description: Experience what it's like to referee the MLS All-Stars against Arsenal! See the game directly from the point-of-view of center referee Ted Unkel as he officiates the 2023 MLS All-Star game between MLS and Arsenal. The REF Cam powered by AT&T 5G allows you to get up close with star players, Christian Benteke, Thiago Almada, Gabriel Jesus and more - running with them on the pitch, arguing calls, and VAR! entry.title: Leagues Cup Shocks: Nashville's VAR Victory Over Club América & Messi's Inter Miami Magic... AGAIN!

media:group.media:title: Leagues Cup Shocks: Nashville's VAR Victory Over Club América & Messi's Inter Miami Magic... AGAIN!
media:group.media:description: Leagues Cup may be many things, but it is never boring. The guys dig into Lionel Messi’s latest masterclass and the quarterfinal matchup with Charlotte, declair LAFC officially back, marvel at the drama in the Clasico Regio and Nashville-Club America matches and draft the craziest moments from the tournament so far! 0:00 - Intro 4:14 - Best things Gass, Wiebe, Doyle and Tommy Scoops saw Round of 16 4:50 - Jim Curtin slams the Red Bulls in press conference 11:08 - Minnesota jump the gun on Club América tickets 14:38 - Nashville’s Panicco comes in to save the PK shootout! 15:53 - Nahuel Guzmán: the GK drama, fun and craziness 24:28 - Dayne St. Claire’s is going full Nahu! 27:43 - Snake draft! Choosing the craziest Leagues Cup’s moments so far 41:52 - Every Inter Miami/Messi game in Leagues Cup is epic! 54:20 - Patrick Agyemang and Charlotte into semis, but do they have a chance vs. Messi?!? 1:01:38 - The Leagues Cup Dark Horse: Querétaro! 1:10:11 - Leagues Cup matchup: Hany v Reynoso! 1:17:01 - LAFC v Monterrey: Denis Bouanga is back! 1:22:04 - Ideal Leagues Cup Final!
